<li><a href="http://cco.cambridge.org/extract?id=ccol0521816262_CCOL0521816262A018" class="external text" title="http://cco.cambridge.org/extract?id=ccol0521816262_CCOL0521816262A018" rel="nofollow">Kathryn Cramer's chapter on hard science fiction in <i>The Cambridge Companion to SF</i></a>, ed. <a href="/wiki/Farah_Mendlesohn" title="Farah Mendlesohn">Farah Mendlesohn</a> &amp; Edward James.</li>
